Test setup
==========
The tests requires that:

1. A D-Bus session bus exists on /tmp/dbus_proxy_outside_socket
Launch with e.g.
$ dbus-daemon --session --nofork --address=unix:path=/tmp/dbus_proxy_outside_socket --print-pid --print-address

2. The outside service is running
$ cd component-test && ./start_outside_service.py

3. The D-Bus proxy is running and listening on /tmp/dbus_proxy_inside_socket
$ cd component-test
$ DBUS_SESSION_BUS_ADDRESS="unix:path=/tmp/dbus_proxy_outside_socket" ../dbus-proxy /tmp/dbus_proxy_inside_socket session < conf_allow_all.json


Running the tests
=================
Tests are exectued using pytest:
$ cd component-test && py.test -vvv test_dbus_proxy.py